information%20about%20the%20events%20and%20later%20offered%20a%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%26quot%3B%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20is%20seeking%20unspecified%20damages%20for%20wrongful%20death%20and%20fraud%2C%20among%20other%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20independently%20verify%20the%20lawsuit's%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20it%20was%20filed%2C%20Fox%20News%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20understand%20the%20grief%20and%20continue%20to%20mourn%20the%20loss%20of%20both%20Pierre%20Zakrzewski%20and%20Sasha%20Kuvshynova%2C%20we%20will%20respectfully%20defend%20against%20the%20inaccurate%20claims%20within%20this%20lawsuit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20safety%20of%20our%20journalists%20has%20always%20been%20our%20number%20one%20priority%20and%20we%20are%20immensely%20grateful%20to%20the%20Fox%20News%20journalists%20who%20have%20covered%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20we%20remain%20committed%20to%20reporting%20from%20the%20region.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20did%20not%20respond%20on%20the%20record%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20details%20of%20the%20alleged%20inaccuracies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECompensation%20with%20a%20catch%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Kuvshynova's%20death%2C%20Fox%20News%20CEO%20Suzanne%20Scott%20contacted%20her%20father%2C%20Andriy%2C%20offering%20her%20condolences%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20day%2C%20Fox%20News'%20HR%20department%20also%20reached%20out%2C%20it%20said%2C%20seeking%20to%20pay%20the%20young%20producer's%20back%20pay%2C%20to%20cover%20her%20funeral%20costs%2C%20and%20to%20offer%20the%20life%20insurance%20coverage%20it%20gives%20to%20its%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20included%20a%20waiver%20with%20confidentiality%20and%20non-disparagement%20clauses%2C%20according%20to%20the%20correspondence%20seen%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20person%20with%20knowled