Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20regretted%20our%20choice%20almost%20immediately.%20Desperate%20for%20the%20freedom%20we'd%20felt%20in%20Denver%2C%20we%20moved%20back%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20(in%202017%2C%20less%20than%20a%20year%20later).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EBecoming%20parents%20made%20finding%20the%20perfect%20home%20feel%20even%20more%20crucial%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Kristen%20Bringe%20and%20her%20husband%20in%20Denver%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6603228c1caec1275a69b092%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EColorado%20isn't%20our%20perfect%20match.%20%3Cp%3EKristen%20Bringe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShortly%20after%20returning%20to%20Denver%2C%20we%20had%20our%20daughter%2C%20which%20raised%20the%20stakes%20in%20our%20search%20for%20place%20perfection.%20We%20wanted%20to%20give%20her%20a%20great%20life%20and%20thought%20finding%20an%20ideal%20place%20to%20do%20so%20was%20essential.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20fantasized%20about%20raising%20her%20in%20an%20idyllic%20setting%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%20but%20our%20eyes%20were%20bigger%20than%20our%20budget%2C%20so%20we%20settled%20for%20what%20we%20hoped%20would%20be%20the%20next%20best%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-move-mountain-towns-housing-affordability-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esmall%20city%20in%20a%20mountainous%20state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20Denver%2C%20we%20moved%20to%20Fort%20Collins%2C%20Colorado%2C%20in%202019%20(which%20didn't%20fit%20the%20bill)%2C%20then%20to%20Bend%2C%20Oregon%2C%20in%202020%20(same)%2C%20and%20then%20back%20to%20Fort%20Collins%20in%202021%20(whoops).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20third%20