ELast%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-just-stepped-up-ai-game-against-google-mustafa-suleyman-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMustafa%20Suleyman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Google's%20DeepMind%2C%20left%20his%20startup%20Inflection%20AI%20to%20lead%20tech%20giant%20Microsoft's%20consumer%20AI%20division%20as%20CEO.%20A%20week%20before%20that%2C%20Aravind%20Srinivas%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Perplexity%2C%20said%20on%20a%20podcast%20he%20couldn't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecruiting-ai-talent-ruthless-right-now-ai-ceo-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoach%20a%20top%20AI%20researcher%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20his%20startup%20didn't%20have%20enough%20GPUs%2C%20Nvidia's%20pricey%20and%20in-demand%20chips.%20Following%20Sam%20Altman's%20brief%20ouster%20from%20OpenAI%20last%20November%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-marc-benioff-poach-openai-talent-x-post-reactions-twitter-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESalesforce%3C%2Fa%3E%20tried%20to%20lure%20researchers%20away%20from%20the%20ChatGPT-maker%20by%20offering%20to%20match%20their%20compensation%20packages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20carousel%20of%20labor%20between%20companies%20illustrates%20the%20high%20demand%20for%20employees%20who%20can%20build%20and%20train%20large%20language%20models%20%E2%80%94%20key%20to%20getting%20AI%20to%20actually%20produce%20the%20results%20firms%20want.%20But%20recruiters%20say%20that%20startups%20and%20smaller%20firms%20struggle%20to%20hire%20workers%20with%20technical%20and%20non-technical%20AI%20skills%2C%20with%20some%20tech%20execs%20believing%20Big%20Tech%20is%20squeezing%20them%20out%20of%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20like%20Meta%20are%20stealing%20away%20and%20holding%20t