0machine%20learning%20engineer%20get%204%25%20of%20the%20startup's%20outstanding%20shares%2C%20which%20used%20to%20be%20completely%20unheard%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20Libre%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThere%20are%20not%20enough%20workers%20with%20AI%20expertise.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20uneven%20financial%20incentives%20aren't%20the%20only%20factor%20in%20the%20battle%20for%20workers.%20Many%20job%20applicants%20simply%20don't%20have%20the%20skills%20for%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20undoubtedly%20a%20shortage%20in%20AI%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20Libre%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20candidates%20for%20generative%20AI%20roles%20include%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20skilled'%20programmers%20and%20data%20scientists%20with%20advanced%20degrees%20who%20are%20well-versed%20in%20programming%20languages%20like%20Python%2C%20Libre%20says.%20They're%20also%20familiar%20with%20deep%20learning%20software%20libraries%20like%20TensorFlow%2C%20Ray%2C%20and%20PyTorch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20recruiter%20says%20companies%20now%20want%20to%20hire%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-ai-freelance-copywriter-editor-novels-memoirs-ebooks-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecopywriters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20product%20managers%2C%20and%20other%20professionals%20who%20may%20not%20have%20a%20technical%20background%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20they%20have%20a%20strong%20grasp%20of%20AI.%20That%20includes%20knowing%20how%20to%20apply%20the%20technology%20to%20workflows%2C%20crafting%20quality%20prompts%2C%20and%20understanding%20bot-generated%20outputs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20combination%20of%20skills%20is%20not%20as%20abundant%20as%20the%20industry%20needs%20and%20not%20as%20abundant%20as%20most%20people%20think%2C%26quot%3B%20Libre%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlavien%20Coronini%2C%20a%20recruiter%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhugging-face-open-source-ai-approach-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3