%20opposition%20convened%20in%20Patna%20to%20devise%20a%20plan%20to%20challenge%20the%20might%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20it%20was%20hailed%20as%20a%20promising%20new%20beginning.%20Despite%20the%20BJP's%20five-year%20tenure%20marked%20by%20controversial%20policies%20such%20as%20demonetisation%2C%20which%20adversely%20affected%20the%20economy%20and%20crippled%20small%20and%20medium-scale%20industries%2C%20leading%20to%20unprecedented%20unemployment%2C%20the%20BJP's%20electoral%20success%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20was%20noteworthy%2C%20surpassing%20the%20300-seat%20mark%20despite%20five%20years%20of%20incumbency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHope%20to%20Despair%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Patna%20conclave%20marked%20a%20promising%20beginning%2C%20then%20the%20meetings%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Mumbai%20infused%20hope%20that%20the%202024%20battle%20would%20be%20tough%20for%20the%20BJP.%20The%20necessary%20buzz%20and%20momentum%20required%20to%20uplift%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20opposition%20and%20those%20disinclined%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20were%20generated.%3Cbr%3E%5CnLeading%20pollsters%20in%20the%20country%20opined%20that%20if%20the%20opposition%20could%20field%20a%20single%20candidate%20against%20the%20BJP%20nationally%20in%20at%20least%20400%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP%20would%20face%20serious%20trouble.%20However%2C%20the%20euphoria%20dissipated%20when%20opposition%20leaders%20convened%20in%20Delhi%20for%20the%20fourth%20conclave%20in%20December.%20The%20Congress%2C%20slated%20to%20lead%20the%20opposition%2C%20suffered%20a%20setback%20due%20to%20significant%20losses%20in%20three%20North%20Indian%20states%20-%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20optimistic%20about%20winning%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20was%20well-positioned%20to%20give%20the%20BJP%20a%20tough%20fight%20in%20Rajasthan.%20The%20lethargy%20of%20the%20Congress%20had%20a%20detrimental%20effect%20on%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20under%20Modi's%20leadership%2C%20seized%20the%20opportunity%20to%20strike%20a%20decisive%20blow.%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20once%20regarded%20as%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20defected%20and%20allied%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20recover%2C%20appearing%20disorganised%20today.%20To%20confront%20the%20formidable%20election%20machinery%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20should%20have%20acted%20swiftly.%20Even%20after%20Nitish's%20defection%2C%20INDIA%20had%20ample%20time%20to%20regroup%20as%20a%20unified%20entity%2C%20but%20it%20seemed%20immobilised.%20Ideally%2C%20if%20it%20was%20genuinely%20committed%20to%20challenging%20and%20defeating%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20should%20have%20pursued%20four%20fronts%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFirstly%2C%20it%20should%20have%20presented%20itself%20as%20a%20unified%20entity%20to%20provide%20an%20alternative%20to%20Modi.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESecondly%2C%20it%20should%20have%20articulated%20an%20alternative%20vision%20document%20for%20the%20nation%2C%20highlighting%20not%20only%20the%20weaknesses%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20but%20also%20offering%20solutions%20to%20the%20country's%20problems.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThirdly%2C%20the%20opposition%20should%20have%20resolved%20seat%20allocations%20among%20themselves%20well%20before%20the%20BJP%20finalised%20its%20list%20of%20candidates.%20The%20opposition%20is%20still%20grappling%20with%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFourthly%2C%20it%20should%20have%20formulated%20a%20cohesive%20communication%20strategy%20to%20counter%20BJP's%20propaganda%20and%20avoided%20speaking%20in%20discordant%20voices.%20It%20should%20have%20prioritised%20keeping%20contentious%20issues%20on%20the%20back%20burner%2C%20akin%20to%20the%20BJP's%20approach%20in%201998%20while%20forming%20a%20coalition%20with%20other%20parties.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Joint%20Manifesto%20Still%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20failed%20on%20all%20the%20four%20fronts%20miserably.%20It%20remains%20uncertain%20if%20there%20will%20be%20a%20joint%20manifesto%20for%20INDIA.%20Instead%20of%20pressuring%20the%20opposition%20parties%20for%20a%20common%20manifesto%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20preoccupied%20with%20offering%20different%20guarantees%20to%20various%20sections%20of%20voters.%20While%20these%20guarantees%20could%20have%20resonated%20well%20with%20the%20people%20and%20created%20a%20buzz%2C%20they%20would%20have%20built%20a%20more%20positive%20narrative%20for%20the%20entire%20opposition%20if%20presented%20from%20a%20unified%20platform%2C%20with%20all%20parties%20and%20leaders%20from%20different%20regions%20endorsing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20politics%2C%20having%20a%20vision%20is%20crucial%2C%20but%20equally%20important%20is%20creating%20a%20vehicle%20through%20which%20that%20vision%20can%20reach%20the%20people.%20Crafting%20a%20vision%20is%20futile%20if%20it%20fails%20to%20reach%20the%20voters%2C%20as%20ultimately%2C%20they%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20choose%20the%20government.%20On%20this%20front%2C%20the%20BJP%20excels%2C%20knowing%20how%20to%20capture%20and%20dominate%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeat%20Distribution%20Troubles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeat%20distribution%20is%20another%20critical%20aspect%20of%20opposition%20unity.%20While%20theoretically%2C%20alliance%20partners%20are%20aligned%20in%20their%20goal%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%2C%20seat%20distribution%20has%20become%20a%20contentious%20issue.%20In%20four%20states%20where%20opposition%20unity%20could%20greatly%20affect%20the%20BJP's%20prospects%20-%20Maharashtra%2C%20Bihar%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Karnataka%20-%20alliance%20partners%20are%20embroiled%20in%20disputes.%20Except%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20is%20contesting%20alone%20and%20is%20well-positioned%2C%20the%20same%20cannot%20be%20said%20for%20the%20other%20three%20states.%20In%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20undermined%20itself.%20The%20bitter%20feud%20between%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20and%20Congress%20leaders%20presents%20a%20poor%20image%20for%20opposition%20politics.%20The%20disparaging%20language%20exchanged%20has%20significantly%20harmed%20the%20image%20of%20INDIA%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%20and%20Bihar%2C%20seat%20distribution%20has%20yet%20to%20be%20finalised.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20under%20Thackeray%2C%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20engaged%20in%20bitter%20battles%20over%20seats%2C%20causing%20tension%20among%20alliance%20partners%20and%20demoralising%20party%20workers.%20Public%20spats%20between%20leaders%20such%20as%20Thackeray%20and%20Congress%20politicians%20negatively%20affect%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%20Bihar%2C%20where%20seat%20distribution%20was%20assumed%20to%20be%20straightforward%20after%20Nitish's%20exit%2C%20negotiations%20have%20proven%20tricky%20and%20problematic.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20nothing%20had%20been%20finalised%20and%20tough%20negotiations%20were%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20INDIA%20failed%20to%20retain%20Jayant%20Chaudhary.%20Although%20seat%20distribution%20has%20been%20finalised%20between%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20no%20joint%20campaign%20has%20been%20launched.%20The%20Congress%20remains%20uncertain%20about%20fielding%20members%20of%20the%20Nehru-Gandhi%20family%20from%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli%2C%20preventing%20the%20finalisation%20of%20its%20candidate%20list%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeaders%20Jumping%20Ships%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20issue%20plaguing%20the%20Congress%20is%20the%20desertion%20of%20party%20leaders%20and%20the%20unwillingness%20shown%20by%20senior%20leaders%20to%20contest%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20doesn't%20imply%20that%20the%20opposition%20has%20surrendered%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Even%20the%20BJP%20faces%20challenges%20with%20its%20alliance%20partners.%20It%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20secure%20alliances%20with%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20in%20Odisha%20and%20the%20Akali%20Dal%20in%20Punjab%2C%20and%20encounters%20problems%20with%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20in%20Karnataka.%20Nonetheless%2C%20the%20BJP%20enjoys%20the%20advantage%20of%20Modi's%20leadership%20and%20the%20formidable%20election%20machinery%20and%20help%20from%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar.%20To%20mount%20a%20significant%20challenge%20and%20overcome%20the%20BJP's%20efficient%20machinery%2C%20the%20opposition%20should%20have%20started%20much%20earlier.%20Instead%2C%20it%20continues%20to%20struggle%2C%20and%20this%20failure%20may%20prove%20costly%20for%20INDIA%20and%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20the%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20Editor%2C%20satyahindi.com)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711545060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F2qb9tqbo_india_625x300_30_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-opposition-unity-forever-in-making-5321307%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20past%20decade%20will%20be%20remembered%20as%20a%20period%20of%20failed%20opposition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-opposition-unity-forever-in-making-5321307%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20interim%20