20of%20two%20Vitality%20Bowl%20a%C3%A7a%C3%AD%20bowl%20restaurants%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20told%20the%20Journal%20he's%20raising%20menu%20prices%20by%20about%2010%25%20to%20cover%20the%20higher%20wages.%20He's%20also%20running%20his%20stores%20with%20two%20employees%2C%20down%20from%20four%2C%20which%20he%20said%20is%20slowing%20down%20order%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20definitely%20not%20going%20to%20hire%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Hom%20told%20the%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVitality%20Bowls%20has%20taken%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20measures%20to%20optimize%20profitability%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20changing%20its%20menu%20and%20improving%20its%20tech%2C%20CEO%20Roy%20Gilad%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement.%20The%20company%20is%20%26quot%3Bwell%20prepared%26quot%3B%20to%20offset%20higher%20costs%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20fast-food%20worker%20who'll%20soon%20be%20getting%20the%20new%20minimum%20wage%3F%20Or%20a%20franchisee%20worried%20about%20how%20it%20will%20affect%20your%20business%3F%20Email%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Agdean%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Egdean%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-fast-food-restaurants-lay-off-workers-minimum-wage-hike-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711542459000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6604038c1caec1275a69cc7b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-fast-food-restaurants-lay-off-workers-minimum-wage-hike-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20Pizza%20Hut%20franchisees%20in%20California%20are%20among%20those%20who%20are%20laying%20off%20workers%2C%20federal%20WARN%20filings%20show.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gdean%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Dean)%2