ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-we-rate-student-loans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20student%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20sitting%20at%20a%20desk%20using%20a%20calculator%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6601e4cf1caec1275a6948f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221050%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYour%20employer%20may%20offer%20additional%20retirement%20benefits%20for%20paying%20your%20student%20loans.%3Cp%3ETom%20Werner%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGetting%20free%20retirement%20funds%20from%20your%20employer%20is%20great%2C%20but%20it%20won't%20be%20useful%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELook%20into%20your%20employer's%20vesting%20schedule%20if%20you%20choose%20to%20use%20this%20benefit.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20CARES%20Act%20also%20allows%20employers%20to%20contribute%20to%20student%20loans%2C%20which%20may%20be%20better.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Secure%202.0%20Act%20brought%20about%20a%20new%20list%20of%20retirement%20plan%20rules%20when%20it%20was%20passed%20into%20law%20in%20December%20of%202022%2C%20although%20some%20of%20the%20legislative%20changes%20didn't%20go%20into%20effect%20until%20the%20beginning%20of%202024.%20This%20includes%20a%20new%20provision%20of%20the%20legislation%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsecure-act-student-loans-retirement-401k-contribution-2023-4%5C%22%3Elets%20employers%20match%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20eligible%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-retirement-plans%5C%22%3Eretirement%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20employee%20payments%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-private-student-loans%5C%22%3Estudent%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployers%20who%20opt%20into%20this%20plan%20can%20consider%20an%20employee's%20student%20loan%20payment%20as%20the%20basis%20for%20an%20employer%20%26quot%3Bmatch%26quot%3B%20into%20an%20eligible%20workplace%20retirement%20plan%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-401k%5C%22%3E401(k)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20paves%20the%20way%20for%20workers%20to%20pay%20down%20student%20debt%20and%20save%20for%20retirement%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20is%20this%20really%20a%20good%20idea%3F%20That%20may%20depend%20on%20who%20you%20ask%20and%20what%20the%20alternatives%20are%2C%20but%20experts%20agree%20there%20are%20upsides%20and%20serious%20downsides%20to%20consider%20for%20workers%20who%20receive%20this%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBorrowers%20with%20limited%20funds%20can%20stretch%20their%20money%20further%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFinancial%20advisor%20Marcel%20Miu%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.simplifywealthplanning.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESimplify%20Wealth%20Planning%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20that%20a%20significant%20advantage%20of%20getting%20student%20loan%20matching%20funds%20into%20a%20retirement%20account%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20build%20retirement%20savings%20even%20while%20focusing%20on%20paying%20down%20student%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20provision%20essentially%20allows%20workers%20to%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20dip%26quot%3B%20with%20their%20student%20loan%20payments%2C%20he%20says%2C%20meaning%20they%20are%20paying%20off%20their%20loans%20while%20simultaneously%20growing%20their%20nest%20egg%20without%20having%20to%20split%20their%20limited%20financial%20resources%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20also%20be%20a%20motivational%20boost%20since%20the%20match%20could%20encourage%20employees%20to%20make%20student%20loan%20payments%20consistently%20since%20they're%20also%20receiving%20some%20benefits%20for%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIt's%20not%20a%20great%20deal%20for%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20borrowers%20are%20repaying%20their%20federal%20student%20loans%20on%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans.%20These%20plans%20base%20student%20loan%20payments%20on%20income%20and%20family%20size%2C%20and%20there%20are%20many%20situations%20where%20borrowers%20with%20relatively%20low%20incomes%20qualify%20for%20a%20%240%20monthly%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20the%20new%20SAVE%20Plan%20from%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20for%20example%2C%20which%20has%20higher%20thresholds%20to%20qualify%20for%20a%20%240%20monthly%20payment%20than%20other%20income-driven%20plans.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ed.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Fbiden-harris-administration-announces-nearly-55-million-borrowers-are-enrolled-save-plan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Department%20of%20Education%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%202.9%20million%20borrowers%20who%20enrolled%20in%20this%20plan%20as%20of%20late%20last%20year%20were%20paying%20%240%20monthly%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20who%20have%20a%20%240%20monthly%20payment%20on%20student%20loans%20wouldn't%20qualify%20to%20receive%20matching%20funds%20to%20retirement%20through%20an%20employer%20with%20this%20provision%20in%20the%20Secure%202.0%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20could%2C%20however%2C%20qualify%20for%20a%20traditional%20match%20on%20contributions%20to%20a%20workplace%20retirement%20plan%20if%20they%20save%20for%20retirement%20and%20their%20employer%20offers%20this%20benefit%20as%20an%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWatch%20out%20for%20vesting%20schedules%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFinancial%20advisor%20Daniel%20Cieniewicz%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhyperionfp.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHyperion%20Financial%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20that%20not%20all%20employers%20have%20chosen%20to%20adopt%20this%20provision%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20interest%20and%20complexity%20surrounding%20the%20law.%20And%20even%20among%20those%20that%20do%2C%20workers%20should%20watch%20out%20for%20vesting%20schedules%20and%20other%20requirements%20to%20receive%20their%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVesting%20percentages%20means%20the%20employer's%20contributions%20may%20require%20an%20employee%20to%20stay%20employed%20at%20the%20company%20in%20order%20to%20have%20the%20employer-contributed%20funds%20%26quot%3Bvest%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20advisor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOtherwise%2C%20if%20an%20employee%20leaves%20prior%20to%20the%20funds%20vesting%2C%20the%20funds%20are%20forfeited%20back%20to%20the%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWatch%20out%20for%20tax%20consequences%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStudent%20loan%20borrowers%20should%20also%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20tax%20consequences%20involved%20in%20accepting%20this%20benefit%20from%20an%20employer%2C%20whether%20good%20or%20bad.%20First%20off%2C%20Miu%20says%20that%20although%20student%20loan%20debt%20is%20paid%20with%20after-tax%20earnings%2C%20there%20is%20a%20student%20loan%20interest%20deduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStudent%20loan%20borrowers%20can%20deduct%20up%20to%20%242%2C500%20in%20interest%20paid%20each%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESingle%20borrowers%20with%20an%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-adjusted-gross-income-agi-taxes%5C%22%3EAGI%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20%2475%2C000%20are%20eligible%20for%20the%20full%20benefit%2C%20as%20are%20joint%20filers%20under%20%24155%2C000.%20The%20ability%20to%20take%20this%20deduction%20phases%20out%20completely%20for%20single%20filers%20who%20earn%20%2490%2C000%20or%20more%20and%20married%20taxpayers%20filing%20jointly%20who%20earn%20%24185%2C000%20or%20more%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20borrowers%20who%20make%20student%20loan%20payments%20may%20be%20able%20to%20deduct%20the%20interest%20they%20pay%20(up%20to%20the%20limits)%20each%20year%2C%20no%20matter%20what.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%20of%20that%2C%20there%20are%20tax%20consequences%20that%20come%20with%20not%20contributing%20directly%20to%20a%20tax-advantaged%20retirement%20account%20like%20a%20401(k).%20Cieniewicz%20points%20out%20that%20pre-tax%20retirement%20plan%20contributions%20lower%20an%20individual's%20adjusted%20gross%20income%2C%20thus%20saving%20on%20federal%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20making%20these%20contributions%20to%20a%20student%20loan%20rather%20than%20a%20retirement%20plan%2C%20you%20could%20be%20forfeiting%20this%20benefit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThere%20are%20alternatives%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20letting%20an%20employer%20match%20student%20loan%20payment%20amounts%20(or%20part%20of%20them)%20into%20an%20eligible%20workplace%20retirement%20plan%20can%20lead%20to%20getting%20%26quot%3Bfree%20money%26quot%3B%20and%20give%20you%20a%20boost%20toward%20retirement%20when%20you%20couldn't%20otherwise%20afford%20to%20save%2C%20there%20are%20other%20ways%20for%20employers%20to%20help%20out%20in%20this%20realm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20Patricia%20Roberts%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgiftofcollege.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGift%20of%20College%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20that%20employers%20can%20also%20make%20direct%20payments%20to%20student%20loans%20for%20their%20workers%20pursuant%20to%20the%20CARES%20Act%20and%20as%20extended%20by%20the%20Consolidated%20Appropriations%20Act%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20permitted%20payments%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstudent-loan-repayment-assistance-workplace-benefits-2022-5%5C%22%3Eup%20to%20%245%2C250%20per%20employee%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20per%20year%20are%20fully%20tax-free%20to%20the%20employee%20on%20whose%20behalf%20they%20are%20made%20and%20can%20be%20made%20through%20December%2031%2C%202025%2C%20unless%20extended%20by%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20offering%20this%20benefit%20wouldn't%20help%20workers%20save%20for%20retirement%2C%20it%20could%20help%20them%20get%20out%20from%20under%20the%20burden%20of%20crushing%20student%20loan%20debt%20considerably%20faster.%20With%20debt%20out%20of%20the%20way%20or%20at%20least%20under%20control%2C%20those%20employees%20may%20have%20more%20bandwidth%20to%20start%20saving%20for%20retirement%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyour-employer-match-student-loan-payments-401k-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711541941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6601e4ca1caec1275a6948ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyour-employer-match-student-loan-payments-401k-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you%20have%20student%20loan%20payments%2C%20your%20employer%20may%20be%20able%20to%20offer%20a%20match%20to%20your%20401(k)%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20a%20perfect%20plan%20for%20every%20borrower.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22holly%40clubthrifty.com%20(Holly%20Johnson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyour-employer-match-student-loan-payments-401k-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHad%20Sensed...%26quot%3B%3A%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Party%20Leader%20On%20Why%20He%20Dumped%20Lalu%20Yadav%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20pre-empted%20attempts%20of%20RJD%20president%20Lalu%20Prasad%20to%20%26quot%3Bhumiliate%26quot%3B%20allies%20ahead%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20by%20calling%20off%20the%20alliance%2C%20a%20senior%20JD(U)%20leader%20claimed%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20Kumar%2C%20MLC%20and%20chief%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20JD(U)%20made%20the%20claim%20referring%20to%20the%20RJD%20riding%20roughshod%20over%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20a%20dependable%20ally%20of%20the%20RJD%2C%20though%20the%20alliance%20has%20caused%20it%20to%20lose%20its%20own%20vote%20share%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20only%20time%20the%20Congress%20saw%20a%20rise%20in%20its%20vote%20share%20in%20recent%20times%20was%20in%20the%202015%20Bihar%20Assembly%20polls%20when%20we%20too%20were%20part%20of%20that%20alliance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20JD(U)%20headed%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERJD%20president%20Lalu%20Prasad%20has%20unilaterally%20given%20party%20tickets%20to%20candidates%20for%20about%20a%20dozen%20seats%20in%20Bihar%2C%20leaving%20the%20Congress%20virtually%20blindsided%20and%20hoping%20against%20hope%20that%20the%20domineering%20ally%20will%20address%20its%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20Kumar%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20type%20of%20alliance%20do%20the%20RJD%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20that%20the%20former%20is%20giving%20away%20party%20tickets%20to%20people%20at%20will%2C%20paying%20scant%20regard%20to%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20latter%3F%26quot%3B%20Among%20the%20seats%20for%20which%20Mr%20Prasad%20has%20given%20tickets%20is%20Aurangabad%2C%20where%20Congress%20wanted%20to%20field%20former%20MP%20Nikhil%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20RJD%20is%20understood%20to%20have%20promised%20party%20ticket%20to%20JD(U)%20turncoat%20Bima%20Bharti%20from%20Purnea%2C%20a%20seat%20from%20which%20former%20MP%20Rajesh%20Ranjan%20alias%20Pappu%20Yadav%20is%20said%20to%20have%20got%20assurance%20of%20Congress%20ticket%20when%20he%20merged%20his%20Jan%20Adhikar%20Party%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20Kumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20not%20for%20nothing%20that%20our%20leader%20Nitish%20Kumar%20had%20been%20seeking%20early%20seat-sharing%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20He%20had%20sensed%20the%20RJD's%20plans%20to%20humiliate%20allies.%20So%20he%20taught%20them%20a%20lesson%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allusion%20was%20to%20Mr%20Kumar's%20exit%20from%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20that%20robbed%20RJD%20of%20power%20and%20stripped%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20son%20and%20heir%20apparent%20of%20Lalu%20Prasad%2C%20of%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFishing%20in%20troubled%20waters%2C%20the%20JD(U)%20leader%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20now%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20show%20that%20it%20has%20spine.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20undertaken%20a%20country-wide%20padayatra%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20leader%20to%20have%20done%20so%20since%20the%201990s%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20that%20in%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20it%20was%20the%20Congress%20that%20managed%20to%20win%20a%20seat%20in%20Bihar%20while%20the%20RJD%2C%20despite%20seeming%20formidable%2C%20drew%20a%20blank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHopefully%2C%20the%20RJD%20will%20be%20taught%20a%20lesson%20by%20its%20ally%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Even%20if%20that%20does%20not%20happen%2C%20the%20party%20will%20be%20taught%20a%20lesson%20by%20the%20people%20of%20Bihar%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MLC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20leaders%20of%20the%20RJD%20and%20the%20Congress%20maintained%20that%20seat-sharing%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bannounced%20in%20an%20amicable%20fashion%26quot%3B%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20joint%20statement%20by%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20and%20BPCC%20president%20Akhilesh%20Prasad%20Singh%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday%20when%20they%20had%20said%20the%20candidates%20will%20be%20formally%20declared%20upon%20their%20return%20to%20Patna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711541880000%2C%2