g-on-remains-of-suicide-bomber-who-killed-5-chinese-nationals%2Farticleshow%2F108819016.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108819016.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPakistani%20authorities%20plan%20DNA%20testing%20on%20remains%20of%20suicide%20bomber%20in%20Shangla%20district%20attack%20that%20killed%205%20Chinese%20nationals%20and%20a%20local%20driver.%20The%20area%20is%20crucial%20for%20China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20with%20workers%20on%20projects%20like%20Dasu%20Dam.%20Pakistan's%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20assured%20a%20prompt%20resolution%20during%20discussions%20with%20the%20Chinese%20ambassador%20Jiang%20Zaidong.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-to-conduct-dna-testing-on-remains-of-suicide-bomber-who-killed-5-chinese-nationals%2Farticleshow%2F108819016.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-to-conduct-dna-testing-on-remains-of-suicide-bomber-who-killed-5-chinese-nationals%2Famp_articleshow%2F108819016.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-to-conduct-dna-testing-on-remains-of-suicide-bomber-who-killed-5-chinese-nationals%2Famp_articleshow%2F108819016.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Stars%20Frustrated%2C%20Militant%20Coach'%3A%20Star%20All-Rounder%20Blasts%20KKR's%20Pandit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChandrakant%20Pandit%20is%20a%20domestic%20cricket%20legend%20in%20India.%20Under%20him%20Mumbai%2C%20Vidarbha%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20enjoyed%20much%20success%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy.%20From%202023%2C%20Pandit%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders.%20Under%20him%2C%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20put%20up%20a%20fighting%20show%20despite%20some%20top%20stars%20missing%20from%20action%20in%20IPL%202023.%20However%2C%20his%20entry%20was%20not%20liked%20by%20several%20overseas%20stars%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22David%20Wiese%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1608-david-wiese-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDavid%20Wiese%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20all%20rounder%20played%20in%20three%20matches%20for%20KKR%20in%20IPL%202023%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20certain%20issues%20going%20on%20behind%20the%20scenes%20in%20the%20team.%20Guys%20weren't%20happy%20with%20certain%20things%20that%20were%20going%20on%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20times%2C%20it%20was%20a%20tough%20changing%20room.%20There%20was%20a%20new%20coach%20coming%20in%20and%20he%20liked%20to%20do%20things%20a%20certain%20way%2C%20and%20that%20didn't%20sit%20well%20with%20the%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20Wiese%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportskeeda.com%2Fcricket%2Fnews-there-certain-issues-behind-scenes-david-wiese-opens-chandu-pandit-s-coaching-style-lows-kkr-s-ipl-2023-campaign%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E'Hitman%20for%20Hire%3A%20A%20year%20in%20the%20life%20of%20a%20franchise%20cricketer'%3C%2Fa%3E%20podcast%20hosted%20by%20Sam%20Keir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20some%20of%20the%20KKR%20stars%20were%20frustrated%20under%20Chandrakant%20Pandit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGuys%20were%20frustrated%20because%20a%20lot%20changed%2C%20and%20the%20coach%20brought%20in%20things%20that%20he%20thought%20would%20bring%20success.%20But%20as%20an%20overseas%20player%2C%20they%20sometimes%20don't%20sit%20well.%20He's%20known%20in%20India%20as%20a%20fairly%20militant%20type%20of%20coach%2C%20a%20strict%20disciplinarian.%20The%20overseas%20guys%20who've%20played%20all%20over%20the%20world%20don't%20need%20someone%20coming%20in%20and%20telling%20him%20how%20to%20behave%20and%20what%20to%20wear%20and%20what%20to%20do.%20I%20was%20chill%20with%20it%2C%20but%20there%20were%20players%20more%20stubborn%20than%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20tournament%20goes%20on%2C%20you%20kind%20of%20sense%20whether%20you%20have%20a%20shot%20at%20qualifying%20or%20not.%20It's%20not%20about%20whether%20you're%20playing%3B%20it's%20just%20about%20spending%20another%20couple%20of%20weeks%20away%20from%20family.%20For%20me%20personally%2C%20the%20result%20of%20the%20game%20didn't%20matter%20that%20much%2C%20but%20I%20still%20got%20pulled%20into%20personal%20performances.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20mentioned%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rinku%20Singh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F106742-rinku-singh-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERinku%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20course%20of%20his%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20player%2C%20you%20appreciate%20it%20when%20guys%20do%20well.%20Rinku%20Singh%20smacks%20five%20sixes%20-%20you%20can't%20not%20appreciate%20that.%20It's%20just%20that%20the%20result%20doesn't%20have%20much%20emphasis%20anymore.%20You%20don't%20sit%20there%20nervous%20about%20whether%20you're%20going%20to%20win.%20And%20you%20start%20investing%20in%20the%20guys'%20personal%20performances%20instead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711537440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fv98lcoto_chandrakant-pandit_625x300_27_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Foverseas-stars-frustrated-militant-coach-star-all-rounder-reveals-unhappy-kkr-dressing-room-in-ipl-2023-5320402%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Under%20Chandrakant%20Pandit%2C%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20put%20up%20a%20fighting%20show%20despite%20some%20top%20stars%20missing%20from%20action%20in%20IPL%202023%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%