rah%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20recounted%20the%20shock%20of%20discovering%20her%20multiple%20pregnancies%20and%20the%20difficult%20decision%20she%20faced%20due%20to%20her%20age.%20Advised%20by%20her%20doctor%20to%20%26quot%3Breduce%26quot%3B%20one%20child%20because%20of%20the%20risks%20associated%20with%20her%20age%2C%20Farah%20said%20that%20she%20bravely%20chose%20to%20proceed%20with%20the%20triplets%20and%20delivered%20her%20three%20bundles%20of%20joy%20-%20Czar%2C%20Anya%2C%20and%20Diva%20in%202008.%20%26quot%3BAt%20ten%20days%20she%20(the%20doctor)%20called%20me%20and%20she%20said%20that%20it's%20triplets%2C%20and%20I%20said%2C%20'Haan%2C%20I%20just%20knew%20it%20doc'.%20Of%20course%20we%20were%20too%20excited%20and%20the%20doctor%20gave%20us%20a%20reality%20check%20and%20said%20that%20we'd%20have%20to%20reduce%20one%20because%20normally%20most%20twins%20start%20out%20as%20triplets.%20She%20said%20that%20you're%20going%20to%20be%2043%20when%20the%20children%20come%20and%20it's%20not%20good%20for%20you.%20Your%20stomach%20is%20great%2C%20your%20lining%20is%20fab%20but%20three%20children%20is%20a%20big%20risk%20and%20one%20child%20can%20be%20really%20small%2C%26quot%3B%20Farah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20playful%20banter%20in%20her%20household%2C%20Farah%20Khan%20shared%20how%20her%20children%20jokingly%20tease%20her%20about%20the%20doctor's%20advice%20to%20%26quot%3Breduce%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20them.%20Farah%20revealed%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20doctor%20gave%20me%20the%20worst%20case%20scenario%2C%20but%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'Doctor%2C%20you%20tell%20me%20what%20you%20need%2C%20how%20big%20you%20want%20each%20child%20to%20be.'%20So%20she%20said%20that%20safely%20they%20should%20be%20two%20kilos%20each.%20I%20said%20I'll%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20are%20over%20and%20above%20that.%20You%20will%20not%20believe%20my%20kids%20were%20two%20and%20a%20half%20kilos%20each.%20So%2C%20I%20was%20literally%20carrying%20seven%20and%20a%20half%20kilos%20and%20roa