l%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rajchandar%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20is%20not%20just%20a%20marvel%20of%20culture%20but%20also%20a%20great%20example%20of%20sustainability.%20From%20composting%20their%20waste%20to%20implementing%20measures%20to%20recharge%20groundwater%2C%20the%20mud%20homestay%20is%20raising%20the%20bar%20for%20nature-friendly%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInspiration%20from%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20home%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Kanyakumari%2C%20Rajchandar%20is%20a%20geo-data%20scientist%20who%20has%20spent%20the%20majority%20of%20his%20life%20around%20environmentalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSpending%20so%20much%20time%20around%20them%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20my%20home%20as%20aligned%20with%20nature%20as%20possible.%20I%20had%20always%20been%20concerned%20about%20the%20degradation%20of%20our%20environment%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20contribute%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajchandar%20fondly%20recalls%20his%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20home%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273684%2Fbest-ecofriendly-homestay-munnar-book-treehouse%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurrounded%20by%20greenery.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20has%20artefacts%20as%20old%20as%20100%20years.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345635%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20homestay%20has%20artefacts%20as%20old%20as%20100%20years.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVisits%20to%20her%20home%20were%20my%20favourite%20part.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20unaware%20of%20how%20her%20deeply%20traditional%20and%20nature-friendly%20home%20would%20one%20day%20become%20an%20inspiration%20for%20my%20dream%20home%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHer%20home%20was%20very%20simple%20with%20minimal%20use%20of%20cement%20and%20very%20traditional%20in%20design%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20living%20in%20the%20city%2C%20he%20longed%20for%20a%20more%20secluded%20place%20surrounded%20by%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20saw%20the%20village%20and%20the%20piece%20of%20land%20which%20now%20holds%20my%20home%2C%20it%20was%20like%20love%20at%20first%20sight.%20I%20could%20envision%20the%20future%20of%20the%20place%20and%20hence%20chose%20to%20buy%20the%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajchandar%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20very%20interesting%20story%20that%20goes%20around%20about%20the%20hills%20surrounding%20the%20area.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20when%20Lord%20Hanuman%20lifted%20the%20Dronagiri%20Parvat%20to%20take%20it%20to%20Lord%20Lakshman%2C%20a%20piece%20of%20it%20broke%20off%20and%20fell%20here.%20Hence%2C%20these%20hills%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20medicinal%20plants%20growing%20around.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20did%20not%20want%20to%20disturb%20the%20biodiversity%20of%20the%20area%20and%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20home%20that%20blends%20into%20nature%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20they%20started%20to%20work%20on%20their%20dream%20home%20and%20opened%20their%20doors%20to%20the%20guests%20in%202022.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20decided%20to%20share%20our%20space%20with%20guests%2C%20we%20have%20hosted%20more%20than%20200%20guests%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMade%20with%20some%20mud%20and%20lots%20of%20love!%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20different%20architectures%2C%20combining%20a%20blend%20of%20Tamil%2C%20Venad%2C%20and%20Chettinad%20styles%20that%20showcase%20the%20rich%20cultural%20heritage%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20personally%20a%20collector%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F309562%2Fancient-family-collectibles-in-pictures-antique-artefacts-projectors-cameras-stamps-coins%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elove%20collecting%20artefacts%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20area.%20I%20had%20been%20collecting%20a%20lot%20of%20art%20pieces%20and%20decided%20to%20display%20them%20in%20the%20home.%20Some%20of%20these%20pieces%20are%20more%20than%20100%20years%20old%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20Rajchandar%20was%20clear%20about%20from%20the%20beginning%20is%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20use%20natural%20materials%20to%20build%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC266EwRIPRB%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC266EwRIPRB%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC266EwRIPRB%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Muthunandhini%20Palace%20(%40muthunandhini_palace)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20just%20want%20to%20have%20sustainable%20practices.%20We%20wanted%20to%20make%20the%20very%20roots%20of%20our%20home%20eco-friendly.%20We%20used%20eco-bricks%20made%20of%20limestone%20and%20red%20clay%20for%20the%20walls%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListing%20all%20the%20natural%20materials%20that%20he%20used%2C%20Rajchandar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBesides%20eco-bricks%2C%20we%20also%20used%20Athangudi%20Tiles.%20These%20tiles%20are%20made%20up%20of%20sand%20found%20near%20Athangudi%20River%20which%20is%20much%20more%20sustainable%20than%20normal%20tiles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20ceiling%2C%20the%20scientist%20used%20a%20technique%20called%20filler%20slab%20technique%20to%20minimise%20the%20use%20of%20concrete.%20According%20to%20Studio%20DCode%2C%20%E2%80%9CFiller%20slab%20is%20an%20alternate%20slab%20construction%20technology%20where%20part%20of%20concrete%20in%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20slab%20is%20replaced%20by%20filler%20material.%E2%80%9D%20The%20roofs%20also%20have%20clay%20tiles%20on%20the%20roofs%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20red%20soil%2C%20lime%2C%20cow%20dung%2C%20rice%20dusk%2C%20egg%20and%20jaggery%20to%20make%20a%20paste%20for%20construction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20homestay%20features%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20and%20they%20are%20in%20the%20process%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F107005%2Fever-wondered-what-a-homemaker-thinks-of-solar-panels%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstalling%20solar%20panels%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20harness%20the%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20make%20compost%20out%20of%20our%20kitchen%20waste%2C%20which%20is%20then%20used%20in%20our%20garden.%20We%20grow%20all%20our%20plants%20and%20food%20organically%20so%20our%20guests%20can%20enjoy%20fresh%20food%20daily.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20place%20boasts%205%20bedrooms%2C%203%20balconies%2C%20and%203%20living%20spaces%20for%20guests%20to%20enjoy.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20homestay%20is%20shared%20by%20us%20with%20the%20guests%2C%20we%20also%20prioritise%20their%20privacy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajchandar%20highlights%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20unique%20feature%20of%20the%20property%20is%20its%20natural%20coolness%20regardless%20of%20the%20weather%20outside.%20With%2050%20upcycled%20windows%20that%20are%20over%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336315%2Fsnow-in-himachal-homestay-vacation-kathkuni-old-manali-restored-house%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E100%20years%20old%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20plenty%20of%20air%20circulates%20inside.%20Additionally%2C%20since%20the%20house%20is%20made%20of%20mud%20and%20clay%2C%20it%20remains%20naturally%20cool%20throughout%20the%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3