e%20contacted%20and%20persuaded%20to%20get%20enrolled%20under%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY.%20We%20also%20mentioned%20that%20due%20procedure%20of%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY%20enrolments%20like%20obtaining%20consent%20forms%2C%20nominee%20details%20etc.%20should%20be%20followed%20by%20branches%20before%20enrolment%20of%20customers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENandy%20said%20a%20bulk%20enrolment%20menu%20was%20especially%20devised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20light%20of%20the%20above%2C%20we%20have%20not%20followed%20any%20unethical%20practice%20while%20enrolling%20customers%20under%20both%20the%20schemes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%E2%80%99s%20customers%20have%20been%20stating%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162226%2FUntitled-2.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22790%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162226%2FUntitled-2.jpeg%20790w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162226%2FUntitled-2-300x117.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-703269%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22307%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0discussed%20these%20allegations%20with%20forensic%20accountant%20and%20certified%20fraud%20examiner%20Nikhil%20Parulkar%2C%20a%20co-founder%20of%20forensic%20advisory%20services%20firm%20Ocurisc%20Consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20UCO%20Bank%20employee%20union%E2%80%99s%20letter%2C%20employees%E2%80%99%20allegations%20and%20online%20complaints%20are%20material%20enough%20to%20warrant%20an%20internal%2Fforensic%20investigation%2C%20which%20would%20entail%20checking%20with%20customers%20whether%20they%20were%20enrolled%20with%20or%20without%20their%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParulkar%20said%20the%20first%20step%20would%20be%20to%20order%20an%20immediate%20stop%20to%20debiting%20customers%E2%80%99%20accounts%20for%20the%20schemes.%20Then%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20internal%20audit%20team%20or%20the%20vigilance%20department%20should%20check%20with%2010%E2%80%9315%25%20of%20randomly%20selected%20customers%20whether%20they%20were%20enrolled%20with%20or%20without%20their%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanara%20Bank%2C%20SBI%20and%20Bank%20of%20Baroda%20did%20not%20reply%20to%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%E2%80%99s%20questions%20about%20enrolling%20customers%20without%20their%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20January%202024%C2%A0%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fsbi-warns-staff-against-enrolling-customers-in-insurance-schemes-without-consent-12126301.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%C2%A0%3Ci%3EMoneyControl%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0showed%20that%20the%20SBI%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20problem%20and%20had%20issued%20a%20letter%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20instructing%C2%A0%20branches%20to%20desist%20from%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20unethical%20practices%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParulkar%20said%20the%20problem%20of%20debiting%20customers%E2%80%99%20accounts%20without%20permission%20for%20one%20or%20the%20other%20schemes%20is%20a%20common%20ailment%2C%20called%20predatory%20sales%20practices%20in%20forensic%20audit%20parlance.%20He%20said%20such%20scenarios%20are%20prevalent%20in%20the%20banking%20sector%2C%20including%20private%20sector%20banks%2C%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20exposed%20until%20a%20whistleblower%20comes%20forth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECanara%20Bank%E2%80%99s%20Cover-Up%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanara%20Bank%20underwent%20an%20audit%20in%20December%202023%20after%20an%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fwealth%2Fpersonal-finance-news%2Fsbi-canara-bank-deducting-premiums-for-govt-insurance-schemes-from-savings-accounts-without-consent-complaints-flood-x%2Farticleshow%2F105646894.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0highlighted%20online%20complaints%20about%20unauthorised%20debits%20for%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%E2%80%99s%20employees%E2%80%99%20grapevine%20was%20abuzz%20with%20news%20about%20this%20audit.%20Purportedly%2C%20the%20government%20asked%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20to%20look%20into%20the%20allegations.%20Subsequently%2C%20branches%20were%20asked%20to%20examine%20customers%E2%80%99%20application%20forms%20for%20these%20schemes.%20Since%20many%20customers%20were%20enrolled%20without%20consent%20via%20bulk%20activation%2C%20their%20forms%20did%20not%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20employee%20said%20his%20regional%20manager%E2%80%94the%20very%20official%20who%20had%20enrolled%20customers%20without%20permission%20in%20bulk%E2%80%94advised%20branch%20heads%20during%20a%20video%20conference%20to%20give%20a%20fake%20confirmation%20that%20the%20forms%20were%20all%20in%20place.%20The%20employee%20said%20his%20branch%20did%20just%20that.%20Eventually%2C%20its%20claim%20was%20accepted%20on%20face%20value%20and%20not%20cross-checked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0has%20a%20copy%20of%20an%20email%20sent%20by%20a%20regional%20office%20of%20the%20bank%20to%20employees%20about%20the%20audit.%20Sent%20on%2029%20December%202023%2C%20it%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CAll%20employees%20are%20advised%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20consent%20forms%20in%20respect%20of%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY%20enrolled%20accounts%20are%20obtained%20and%20placed%20on%20records.%20Inspection%20wing%20has%20given%20a%20timeline%20up%20to%2030.12.2023%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20consent%20letter%20from%20customers%20has%20been%20obtained%20invariably%20and%20kept%20on%20record.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20branch%20manager%20of%20Canara%20Bank%20posted%20in%20central%20India%20recounted%20that%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20his%20regional%20office%20enrolled%2050-odd%20customers%20of%20his%20branch%20in%20PMJJBY%20from%20the%20back-end%2C%20without%20consent.%20He%20said%20that%20to%20save%20himself%20from%20any%20trouble%20later%20on%2C%20he%20obtained%20application%20forms%20from%20most%20of%20the%20customers%20over%20the%20next%20few%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20aforesaid%20audit%20that%20followed%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0report%2C%20Canara%20Bank%20employees%20were%20required%20to%20pull%20off%20a%20similar%20feat%2C%20in%20one%20day.%20About%20two%20weeks%20after%20the%20bank%20asked%20its%20employees%20over%20email%20to%20obtain%20consent%20forms%2C%20a%20bank%20officer%20told%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0via%20WhatsApp%20that%20the%20management%20was%20turning%20on%20the%20heat.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20application%20pressure%20is%20real.%20I%20feel%20like%20resigning%20%5Bfrom%5D%20the%20job.%20What%20the%20heck!%20Someone%20from%20the%20back-end%20did%20something%2C%20now%20they%20are%20asking%20us%20to%20clean%20that%20mess.%20How%20am%20I%20going%20to%20get%204%2C000%20forms!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20employee%20later%20said%20she%20did%20not%20arrange%20for%20the%20forms%20as%20the%20pressure%20for%20the%20same%20vanished.%20Canara%20Bank%20did%20not%20reply%20to%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%E2%80%99s%20questions%20about%20this%20audit%20and%20the%20aforesaid%20email.%20Forensic%20auditor%20Parulkar%20said%20the%20email%20unambiguously%20pointed%20at%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWherever%20we%20have%20enrolled%20without%20asking%2C%20create%20a%20paper%20trail%20for%20that%20and%20place%20it%20on%20record.%20That%20is%20how%20this%20email%20has%20to%20be%20read%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20is%20a%20fraudulent%20practice%20tantamount%20to%20doctoring%20a%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPressure%20From%20The%20Top%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20pressure%2C%20bank%20employees%20do%20not%20blame%20their%20management%20as%20much%20as%20they%20blame%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinancialservices.gov.in%2Fbeta%2Fen%2Fpage%2Foverview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Financial%20Services%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(DFS)%2C%20which%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20key%20initiatives%20of%20the%20government%20concerning%20the%20banking%20and%20insurance%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20PMJJBY%2C%20PMSBY%2C%20APY%20and%20other%20government%20schemes%2C%20the%20DFS%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDFS_India%2Fstatus%2F1758119464762028102%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egives%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0enrolment%20targets%20to%20banks.%20Bank%20employees%20told%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0that%20top%20executives%20are%20berated%20by%20the%20DFS%20and%20threatened%20with%20consequences%20for%20failing%20to%20meet%20the%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20letter%20issued%20by%20government-run%20Punjab%20%26amp%3B%20Sind%20Bank%20to%20a%20zonal%20manager%20illustrates%20this%20top-down%20pressure.%20The%20letter%20cites%20the%20DFS%E2%80%99s%20order%20about%20these%20insurance%20and%20pension%20schemes%2C%20notes%20that%20the%20zonal%20manager%E2%80%99s%20area%20is%20lagging%20behind%2C%20and%20ends%20with%20a%20warning%3A%20the%20targets%20are%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cmandatorily%20achieved%E2%80%9D%20to%20avoid%20%E2%80%9Cany%20unpleasant%20action%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20497px)%2085vw%2C%20497px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162327%2FUntitled-3.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22