20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20SBI%20kiosk%20operator%20from%20rural%20Bihar%20told%20this%20reporter%20that%20his%20seniors%20have%20been%20ordering%20every%20day%20in%20online%20meetings%20to%20meet%20the%20targets%20assigned%20by%20the%20DFS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20seniors%20advise%20arm-twisting%20customers%20into%20signing%20up%20and%20also%20threaten%20kiosk%20operators%20with%20loss%20of%20pay.%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Fhow-an-aadhaar-fraud-forces-the-poor-into-paying-for-welfare-schemes-they-do-not-want-63f57eb9e8d15%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevious%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0explains%20how%20these%20dynamics%20lead%20to%20widespread%20fraud%20with%20rural%20customers.%20A%20report%20in%20Hindi%20daily%C2%A0%3Ci%3EDainik%20Bhaskar%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0on%2017%20March%20described%20how%20an%20SBI%20kiosk%20operator%20in%20rural%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20fraudulently%20enrolled%20customers%20in%20PMSBY%20and%20registered%20their%20dead%20fathers%20as%20nominees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0sought%20comment%20from%20the%20DFS%20and%20the%20union%20finance%20ministry%20via%20email%20on%202%20March.%20There%20was%20no%20reply.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20response%2C%20we%20will%20update%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0filed%20an%20RTI%20request%20with%20the%20department%20and%20sought%20a%20copy%20of%20its%20letters%2Fcirculars%20to%20banks%20regarding%20enrollment%20under%20PMJJBY%2C%20PMSBY%20and%20APY.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20refused%20the%20information%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20information%20sought%20is%20under%20deliberation%20with%20the%20concerned%20stakeholders.%20The%20information%20received%20or%20generated%20is%20in%20fiduciary%20capacity%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20affect%20and%20compromise%20the%20strategic%20and%20economic%20interests%20of%20the%20State.%20The%20disclosure%20of%20such%20information%20is%20likely%20to%20affect%20the%20decision-making%20of%20the%20authority.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmployees%20of%20various%20government%20banks%20explained%20to%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Ehow%20the%20pressure%20for%20these%20schemes%20percolates%20from%20the%20management%20to%20ground-level%20staff%20and%20results%20in%20fraud.%20Requesting%20anonymity%2C%20a%20mid-level%20officer%20of%20a%20government%20bank%20recounted%20a%20first-hand%20experience%20from%20his%20stint%20in%20a%20regional%20office%3A%20high%20enrolment%20targets%20for%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY%20were%20imposed%20upon%20managers%2C%20eight%20of%20whom%20fell%20short%2C%20so%20they%20were%20lambasted%20in%20a%20meeting%20and%20their%20salary%20docked%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20once%20discussed%20with%20his%20senior%2C%20an%20assistant%20general%20manager%2C%20his%20apprehensions%20about%20debiting%20customers%E2%80%99%20accounts%20without%20consent.%20He%20said%20the%20official%20dismissed%20his%20concerns%20and%20told%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EKya%20fark%20padta%20hai!%20Kuch%20nahi%20hoga.%20Sab%20upar%20se%20neeche%20tak%20government%20ka%20saath%20hai%3C%2Fi%3E.%E2%80%9D%20(How%20does%20it%20matter!%20Nothing%20will%20happen.%20From%20the%20top%20to%20the%20bottom%2C%20we%20have%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20backing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20gauge%20the%20extent%20of%20fraudulent%20enrolments%2C%20this%20reporter%20created%20a%20poll%20in%20three%20Facebook%20groups%20of%20bank%20employees.%20One%20group%20was%20the%20bank%20union%20We%20Bankers%2C%20and%20the%20other%20two%20were%20private%20groups%20for%20employees%20of%20Punjab%20National%20Bank%20(PNB)%20and%20Canara%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20428%20people%20who%20voted%2C%20more%20than%2091%25%20said%20that%20either%20they%20or%20their%20colleagues%20were%20under%20pressure%20from%20their%20seniors%20to%20enrol%20customers%20in%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY%20by%20hook%20or%20by%20crook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162614%2FUntitled-4.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22725%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162614%2FUntitled-4.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162614%2FUntitled-4-300x146.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162614%2FUntitled-4-1024x498.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-703271%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22353%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBank%20employees%E2%80%99%20Facebook%20groups%20are%20full%20of%20posts%20and%20discussion%20threads%20about%20having%20to%20fraudulently%20enrol%20customers%20in%20these%20schemes.%20Photo%20courtesy%20Article%2014%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Facebook%20as%20well%20as%20X%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAnAamEmployee%2Fstatus%2F1672083609610756097%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBachaoBank%2Fstatus%2F1741452466422768037%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRRBvaleMAZDOOR%2Fstatus%2F1687168183449616384%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20bank%20employees%20have%20been%20decrying%20the%20pressure%20and%20arm-twisting%20to%20enrol%20customers%20in%20these%20schemes%20without%20their%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECustomers%20Hit%20Back%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20insurance%20schemes%20are%20low-cost%20and%20beneficial%2C%20unauthorised%20debits%20for%20the%20same%20have%20annoyed%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EX%20is%20awash%20with%20complaints%20of%20such%20customers%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20students%2C%20unemployed%20youth%20and%20the%20poor%2C%20for%20whom%20every%20rupee%20matters.%20Some%20people%20have%20posted%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20220724041558%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsanket_sirsat%2Fstatus%2F1550877329810792448%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20220826054520%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsatya2192%2Fstatus%2F1534433423753785344%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E)%20that%20their%20account%20balance%20has%20gone%20into%20negative%20because%20of%20these%20unauthorised%20and%20unplanned%20deductions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20of%20these%20unauthorised%20debits%20can%20be%20ascertained%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20YouTube%20videos%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCfK0MTHVTAQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5ByLGllXPHk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNJo1bN5NgOk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E)%20about%20how%20to%20exit%20these%20schemes%20garner%20lakhs%20of%20views%20and%20hundreds%20of%20angry%20comments%20from%20aggrieved%20bank%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Canara%20Bank%20customer%20from%20Karnataka%20is%20suing%20the%20bank%20for%20debiting%20his%20account%20without%20consent%20for%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY.%20In%20a%20case%20filed%20with%20Dharwad%20district%20consumer%20forum%20last%20July%2C%20Kiran%20M%20Goli%20sought%20Rs%205%20lakh%20as%20damages%20for%20breach%20of%20fiduciary%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoli%20told%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0over%20a%20phone%20call%20that%20the%20bank%20offered%20to%20settle%20the%20matter%20outside%20the%20court%20for%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%20an%20offer%20he%20rejected.%20He%20said%20he%20is%20pursuing%20the%20case%20not%20for%20money%20but%20for%20drawing%20the%20judiciary%E2%80%99s%20attention%20to%20this%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20planned%20to%20file%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20request%20a%20forensic%20audit%20into%20all%20banks%E2%80%99%20enrolment%20modalities%20for%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoli%20said%20Canara%20Bank%20granted%20him%20a%20refund%20for%20unsolicited%20insurance.%20The%20bank%20reportedly%20told%20him%20it%20intended%20to%20debit%20somebody%20else%E2%80%99s%20account%20but%20his%20account%20was%20charged%20because%20of%20a%20technical%20error.%20The%20bank%20gave%20the%20same%20explanation%20to%20another%20customer%20from%20Rajasthan%20who%20had%20filed%20an%20RTI%20request%20in%20July%202023%20to%20ask%20how%20his%20account%20got%20charged%20for%20these%20schemes.%20The%20bank%E2%80%99s%20RTI%20reply%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20some%20technical%20error%2C%20your%20account%20was%20debited%20for%20some%20amount%20instead%20of%20the%20other%20account.%20The%20deduction%20was%20totally%20a%20technical%20error.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20same%20lines%2C%20SBI%20replied%20to%20an%20RTI%20query%20of%20a%20Bihar%20resident%20last%20June%20by%20saying%20that%20his%20account%20was%20debited%20for%20PMJJBY%20erroneously.%20This%20reporter%20knows%20of%20banks%20giving%20the%20same%20reply%20to%20other%20customers%E2%80%99%20RTI%20requests%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20584px)%2085vw%2C%20584px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162739%2F5-SBI-RTI.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22584%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162739%2F5-SBI-RTI.jpeg%20956w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F26162739%2F5-SBI-RTI-300x263.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-703272%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESBI%E2%80%99s%20reply%20to%20its%20customers%20who%20sought%20their%20PMJJBY%20and%20PMSBY%20enrolment%20forms%20under%20the%20RTI%20Act%20after%20the%20bank%20charged%20their%20accounts%20without%20permission%20for%20these%20schemes.%20Photo%20courtesy%20Article%2014%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECertified%20fraud%20examiner%20Parulkar%20said%20that%20with%20many%20frauds%20that%20do%20take%20place%20in%20banks%2C%20especially%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20it%20is%20observed%20that%20a%20cover-up%20can%20be%20pulled%20off%20by%20portraying%20the%20fraud%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctechnical%E2%80%9D%20error.%20He%20said%20banks%20generally%20try%20to%20get%20away%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20technicality.%20He%20said%20that%20while%20the%20benefit%20of%20doubt%20must%20be%20extended%20to%20everyone%20under%20the%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice%2C%20banks%20tend%20to%20use%20this%20tenet%20as%20a%20shield%20to%20hide%20their%20malpractices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20customers%20demand%20a%20refund%2C%20at%20times%20bank%20employees%20pay%20them%20from%20their%20own%20pocket%20to%20avoid%20hassles.%20A%20PNB%20customer%20from%20Punjab%20said%20her%20branch%20manager%20paid%20her%20in%20cash%20and%20made%20the%20entry%20manually%20in%20her%20passbook.%C2%A0%3Cb%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0has%20seen%20the%20passbook%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20an%20SBI%20employee%20from%20rural%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20offered%20to%20give%20a%20refund%20to%20a%20student%20from%20his%20own%20pocket%20after%20the%20student%20filed%20an%20RTI%20request%20and%20sought%20his%20enrolment%20forms.%20This%20reporter%20has%20the%20call%20recording%20in%20which%20the%20bank%20employee%20can%20be%20heard%20requesting%20the%20student%20to%20accept%20the%20money%20and%20let%20go%20of%20the%20matter%2C%20or%20else%20the%20employee%20would%20be%20in%20the%20line%20of%20fire.%20The%20student%20refused%20to%20accept%20money%20from%20the%20employee%20and%20insisted%20that%20the%20bank%20refund%20him%2C%20a%20request%20that%20was%20ultimately%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBank%20employees%20told%20this%20reporter%20that%20the%20unrelenting%20pressure%20to%20add%20customers%20in%20these%20schemes%20has%20been%20taking%20a%20toll%20on%20them.%20Refusing%20to%20enrol%20customers%20through%20easy%20but%20illegal%20methods%20can%20earn%20the%20ire%20of%20seniors%20whereas%20a%20complaint%20of%20wrongful%20enrolment%20from%20a%20customer%20can%20be%20a%20blot%20on%20their%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%2026%20April%202023%2C%20more%20than%2016.19%20crore%20people%20stood%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1922622%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esubscribed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20PMJJBY%20and%20more%20than%2034.18%20crore%20stood%20subscribed%20to%20PMSBY.%20Bank%20employees%20contend%20that%20if%20a%20forensic%20audit%20is%20undertaken%2C%20most%20of%20these%20registrations%20will%20turn%20out%20to%20have%20been%20done%20without%20customers%E2%80%99%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EHemant%20Gairola%20is%20an%20independent%20journalist%20based%20in%20Dehradun.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Fbanks-want-forged-paper-trails-after-taking-money-illegally-from-cu