%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F66016e55230000a828657612.jpeg%3Fcache%3D6uUrPmnXtS%26ops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fboeing-ceo-dave-calhoun-will-step-down-by-end-of-year_n_66016e46e4b059750143c4e0%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Boeing%20has%20been%20under%20intense%20pressure%20since%20early%20January%2C%20when%20a%20panel%20blew%20off%20a%20brand-new%20Alaska%20Airlines%20737%20Max.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A341%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fboeing-ceo-dave-calhoun-will-step-down-by-end-of-year_n_66016e46e4b059750143c4e0%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fboeing-ceo-dave-calhoun-will-step-down-by-end-of-year_n_66016e46e4b059750143c4e0%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fboeing-ceo-dave-calhoun-will-step-down-by-end-of-year_n_66016e46e4b059750143c4e0%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brothers%20Brave%20Family%20Pressure%20to%20Farm%20Mushrooms%2C%20Now%20Earn%20Rs%207.5%20Cr%20Annually%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20kid%20is%20asked%20what%20they%20want%20to%20become%20when%20they%20grow%20up%2C%20the%20usual%20answers%20are%20either%20a%20doctor%2C%20pilot%2C%20lawyer%2C%20or%20engineer.%20What%20is%20uncommon%20to%20hear%20is%20that%20they%20want%20to%20become%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20cities%2C%20away%20from%20farms%2C%20most%20children%20are%20not%20even%20aware%20of%20where%20their%20food%20comes%20from.%20However%2C%20for%20Rishabh%20and%20Ayush%20Gupta%2C%20two%20brothers%20from%20Agra%2C%20it%20was%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20and%20grandfather%20were%20both%20very%20interested%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342922%2Fhow-to-do-pearl-farming-in-artificial-ponds-in-rajasthan-computer-teacher-reaps-huge-profits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20agriculture%20and%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20we%20were%20young%2C%20my%20father%20even%20tried%20his%20hand%20at%20polyhouse%20farming%20but%20was%20not%20able%20to%20take%20it%20through.%20Since%20then%2C%20my%20brother%20and%20I%20have%20been%20interested%20in%20the%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ayush%20says%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20the%20duo%20run%20an%20organic%20polyhouse%20farm%20in%20Agra%20growing%2016%20varieties%20of%20vegetables%20and%20mushrooms.%20Their%20business%20has%20been%20soaring%20with%20success%2C%20selling%20more%20than%20Rs%201%20lakh%20worth%20of%20products%20every%20day.%20Their%20farm%20produces%2040%20tonnes%20of%20mushrooms%20and%2045%20tonnes%20of%20vegetables%20every%20month!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntrigued%20about%20how%20they%20do%20it%3F%20Here%20is%20what%20they%20have%20to%20say%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20our%20father%E2%80%99s%20dreams%20come%20true%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Delhi%2C%20Ayush%20(25)%20and%20Rishabh%20(27)%20grew%20up%20watching%20their%20father%20dream%20of%20pursuing%20polyhouse%20farming.%20The%20family%20moved%20to%20Agra%20in%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolyhouse%20farming%2C%20also%20referred%20to%20as%20greenhouse%20farming%20or%20protected%20cultivation%2C%20involves%20growing%20crops%20within%20a%20controlled%20environment.%20Polyhouses%2C%20constructed%20from%20transparent%20materials%20like%20polyethene%20or%20polycarbonate%2C%20permit%20sunlight%20penetration%20while%20trapping%20heat%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20working%20and%20could%20not%20dedicate%20full%20attention%20to%20it.%20He%20suggested%20my%20grandfather%20take%20it%20up%2C%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20either.%20So%2C%20he%20always%20harboured%20this%20wish%2C%20and%20when%20my%20brother%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20venture%20into%20it%2C%20we%20knew%20where%20to%20start%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ayush.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20began%20when%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CBack%20then%2C%20I%20was%20in%20London%20studying%20BBA%2C%20and%20my%20brother%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296139%2Ftamil-nadu-man-quits-dubai-job-to-revive-water-bodies-help-lakhs-after-cyclone-india-water-warriors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudying%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fa%3E%20We%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20coming%20back%20home%20that%20year%2C%20but%20I%20had%20to%20return%20due%20to%20the%20lockdown%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-1-1710404096.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ayush%20and%20Rishabh%20Gupta%2C%20founders%20of%20A33%20Mushroom%20Farms%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-1-1710404096.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-1-1710404096-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-1-1710404096-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-1-1710404096-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-1-1710404096-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344843%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAyush%20and%20Rishabh%20Gupta%2C%20founders%20of%20A33%20Mushroom%20Farms.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20my%20brother%20was%20stuck%20in%20Dubai%20due%20to%20travel%20restrictions.%20It%20was%20during%20that%20time%20that%20he%20started%20feeling%20lonely%20and%20wanted%20to%20come%20back%20home.%20He%20realised%20that%20he%20needed%20to%20be%20near%20his%20family.%20So%2C%20during%20our%20conversations%2C%20he%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20return%20to%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202020%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340041%2Fentrepreneur-save-family-business-harshit-tanay-agrawal-pistabarfi-cloud-kitchen-janta-dairy-sweets-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20brothers%20reunited%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20decided%20not%20to%20go%20back%20to%20either%20London%20or%20Dubai%20and%20instead%20stay%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20always%20discuss%20how%2C%20if%20we%20ever%20became%20business%20persons%2C%20we%20would%20enter%20the%20food%20industry.%20However%2C%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20passion%20towards%20having%20a%20farm%20motivated%20us%20to%20try%20our%20hand%20at%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20brothers%E2%80%99%20decision%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F320228%2Fpune-brothers-quit-job-to-start-organic-farming-venture-worth-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecome%20farmers%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20not%20well-received%20by%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20uncommon%20in%20Indian%20households%20for%20the%20relatives%20to%20have%20strong%20opinions.%20My%20father%20was%20told%20that%20he%20has%20put%20so%20much%20money%20into%20our%20education%20and%20sent%20us%20abroad%20for%20nothing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisheartened%20by%20the%20reaction%2C%20it%20was%20his%20father%20that%20gave%20them%20the%20courage.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20told%20us%20that%20we%20need%20not%20list