%2Fwomen-empowerment-7-1710768940-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-7-1710768940-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-7-1710768940-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345107%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20self-help%20groups%20are%20not%20only%20a%20way%20for%20women%20to%20take%20on%20leadership%20roles%20but%20also%20to%20be%20financially%20independent%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Rashmi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20would%20the%20village%20women%20be%20interested%20in%20this%20foreign%20concept%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20week%2C%2050%20women%20of%20the%20village%20responded%20to%20an%20ad%20that%20Sawant%20had%20put%20out%20in%20the%20local%20paper%20about%20her%20idea%2C%20effectively%20answering%20her%20question.%20Out%20of%20the%20group%2C%20two%20women%20raised%20their%20hands%20when%20Sawant%20enquired%20how%20many%20would%20like%20to%20turn%20their%20homes%20into%20homestays.%20One%20of%20the%20first%20families%20to%20show%20interest%20was%20a%20couple%2C%20Vaishali%20and%20Vijay%20Loke.%20Today%2C%20their%20homestay%2C%20%E2%80%98Pitruchaya%E2%80%99%20in%20Devgad%2C%20is%20a%20thriving%20success.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20homestay%2C%20%E2%80%98Nandan%20Farms%E2%80%99%20at%20Sawantwadi.%20run%20by%20Amruta%20Padgaonkar%20is%20also%20amassing%20great%20love%20from%20tourists%20who%20are%20keen%20to%20spend%20their%20vacation%20at%20an%20authentic%20mud%20homestay.%20The%20locals%20weren%E2%80%99t%20left%20alone%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20intricacies%20of%20running%20a%20homestay%20business.%20Sawant%20hand-held%20them%20through%20the%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20got%20professional%20experts%20to%20come%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%