ds%20of%20these%20birds%20flock%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESawant%20organised%2020%20women%20into%20self-help%20groups%20that%20would%20conduct%20and%20benefit%20from%20bird%20tourism.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20women%20were%20trained%20to%20take%20the%20tourists%20around%20the%20village%2C%20explain%20to%20them%20about%20these%20birds%20and%20their%20migration%20patterns%20and%20show%20them%20their%20nests.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Sawant%20looks%20back%20on%20how%20she%20has%20succeeded%20in%20bridging%20the%20gap%20between%20tourists%20looking%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F308710%2Ftentgram-provides-experiential-travel-across-india-wayanad-kashmir-meghalaya-himachal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperiential%20travel%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20one%20side%20and%20villagers%20looking%20to%20earn%20on%20the%20other%2C%20she%20smiles%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20a%20vision%20to%20help%205%2C000%20women%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years.%20Because%20every%20woman%20empowered%20is%20a%20family%20empowered.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711353859000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment--1710768304.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345085%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rashmi%20Sawant%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20'Culture%20Aangan'%2C%20an%20experiential%20travel%20platform%20that%20aims%20to%20promote%20sustainable%20rural%20tourism%20and%20support%20grass%20root%20development%20projects%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Sindhudurg%20district%20of%20Maharashtra.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345085%2Feco-tourism-helps-rural-woman-earn-mangroves-of-sindhudurg-rashmi-sawant-homestays-konkan%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Startup%E2%80%99s%20Innovation%20Could%20Help%20Millions%20Get%20Access%20to%20Better%20Brain%20Health%20At%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsaac%20John%E2%80%99s%20father%20was%20first%20diagnosed%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329667%2Fpalghar-kiran-kamdar-free-homemade-khichdi-for-patients-hospital-parkinson-disease%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParkinson%E2%80%99s%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202016.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Issac%20was%20on%20a%20brief%20sabbatical%20from%20his%20corporate%20life%20in%20Bengaluru%20while%20his%20father%20was%20working%20in%20Vapi%2C%20Gujarat.%20Witnessing%20his%20father%20struggle%20with%20this%20neurodegenerative%20condition%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Issac%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20began%20with%20involuntary%20shaking%20of%20his%20hands%20without%20anyone%20taking%20note%20of%20it.%20We%20waited%20for%20months%20before%20seeking%20medical%20input.%20He%20was%20put%20on%20a%20medicine%20called%20Syndopa%20that%20continued%20throughout%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20life%20along%20with%20certain%20vitamin%20supplements.%20While%20he%20worked%20for%20another%20year%20after%20his%20first%20diagnosis%2C%20driving%20a%20car%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20things%20he%20had%20to%20give%20up%2C%20and%20subsequently%2C%20his%20job%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20time%2C%20Issac%E2%80%99s%20father%20was%20compelled%20to%20move%20to%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Kerala%20and%20live%20with%20their%20joint%20family.%20Since%20then%2C%20they%20had%20to%20engage%20in%20%E2%80%98steady%20management%E2%80%99%20of%20his%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20received%20little%20guidance%20on%20what%20diet%20or%20lifestyle%20would%20help%20him%20cope%20better.%20Living%20in%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Kerala%2C%20access%20to%20high-quality%20neurological%20experts%20was%20also%20limited.%20Our%20family%20and%20I%20accepted%20the%20status%20quo%20and%20slowly%20he%20withdrew%20from%20other%20social%20activities.%20He%20wanted%20to%20resume%20work%20in%20some%20way%2C%20but%20the%20shaking%20of%20the%20hands%20transferred%20to%20the%20legs%20as%20well%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20and%20he%20had%20to%20have%20someone%20around%20for%20mobility%20around%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20a%20point%2C%20the%20medication%20did%20little%20to%20improve%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20quality%20of%20life%3B%20seeing%20it%20deteriorate%20like%20that%20despite%20the%20medication%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20Isaac.%20Tragically%2C%20he%20passed%20away%20in%202020%20amid%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Rahul%20Krishnan%2C%20who%20comes%20from%20a%20large%20joint%20family%20in%20Ernakulam%2C%20Kerala%2C%20also%20witnessed%20firsthand%20the%20struggles%20of%20loneliness%20and%20isolation%20among%20his%20older%20relatives%2C%20particularly%20those%20dealing%20with%20neurodegenerative%20conditions.%20With%20the%20added%20strain%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20there%20was%20news%20every%20day%20of%20someone%E2%80%99s%20cognitive%20health%20in%20the%20family%20deteriorating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Rahul%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20come%20from%20a%20large%20joint%20family%20in%20Kerala.%20Like%20me%2C%20many%20of%20my%20cousins%20and%20friends%20ventured%20away%20from%20home%20in%20pursuit%20of%20better%20educational%20and%20career%20prospects.%20With%20the%20rise%20of%20nuclear%20families%2C%20meeting%20elders%20became%20a%20yearly%20affair%20at%20best.%20But%20witnessing%20the%20rapid%20ageing%20and%20forgetfulness%20of%20our%20loved%20ones%20has%20always%20made%20me%20wonder%20why%20there%20are%20no%20tools%20for%20early%20detection%20of%20memory%20decline.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20encouraged%20my%20father%20to%20play%20sudoku%20and%20solve%20puzzle%20books%20to%20keep%20his%20mind%20sharp%20and%20active%2C%20I%20recognised%20a%20latent%20concern%20in%20almost%20every%20family%20like%20mine.%20The%20realisation%20that%20there%20is%20a%20significant%20gap%20in%20awareness%20and%20access%20to%20resources%20aimed%20at%20understanding%20and%20arresting%20cognitive%20decline%20served%20as%20a%20key%20driving%20force%20behind%20the%20inception%20of%20%E2%80%98Ivory%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20meeting%20each%20other%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20July%202022%20during%20a%20residency%20programme%20for%20aspiring%20entrepreneurs%20run%20by%20Antler%2C%20an%20early-stage%20venture%20capitalist%20(VC)%20firm%2C%20Issac%20and%20Rahul%20would%20come%20together%20to%20establish%20%E2%80%98Ivory%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%20October%202022%2C%20this%20Mumbai-based%20%E2%80%98age-tech%E2%80%99%20startup%20is%20working%20towards%20redefining%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20ageing%20experience%E2%80%9D%20by%20focusing%20on%20%E2%80%9Cbetter%20brain%20health%20through%20neuroscience-backed%20assessments%2C%20interactive%20games%2C%20and%20personalised%20solutions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIssac-John-and-Rahul-Krishnan-Founder-1711111144.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Co-founders%20of%20Ivory%3A%20Issac%20John%20and%20Rahul%20Krishnan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIssac-John-and-Rahul-Krishnan-Founder-1711111144.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIssac-John-and-Rahul-Krishnan-Founder-1711111144-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIssac-John-and-Rahul-Krishnan-Founder-1711111144-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIssac-John-and-Rahul-Krishnan-Founder-1711111144-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIssac-John-and-Rahul-Krishnan-Founder-1711111144-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345585%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECo-founders%20of%20Ivory%3A%20Issac%20John%20and%20Rahul%20Krishnan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20common%20ground%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20and%20Issac%20hail%20from%20different%20small%20towns%20in%20Kerala.%20Their%20shared%20experience%20of%20being%20away%20in%20metropolitan%20cities%20for%20their%20careers%20while%20their%20parents%20stayed%20back%20in%20Kerala%20became%20a%20key%20reason%20for%20them%20to%20bond%20over%20the%20problems%20of%20the%20elderly%20that%20led%20to%20Ivory%E2%80%99s%20founding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20starting%20point%20was%20to%20build%20something%20that%20would%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335260%2Fshantanu-naidu-startup-the-goodfellows-helps-senior-citizens-connect-with-youth-ratan-tata%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20parents%20feel%20less%20isolated%20and%20lonely%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20stayed%20away%20from%20their%20children.%20During%20the%20course%20of%20our%20research%2C%20we%20understood%20that%20loneliness%20and%20isolation%20increase%20risks%20of%20neurodegeneration%20by%20over%2050%25%2C%20especially%20in%20collectivist%20societies%20like%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Issac.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20made%20us%20look%20into%20this%20space%20more%20closely.%20The%20more%20we%20spoke%20to%20people%2C%20we%20realised%20losing%20memory%20was%20a%20widespread%20concern%20that%20many%20people%20vocalised%20but%20had%20little%20direction%20on%20what%20to%20do%20about%20it.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20we%20zeroed%20in%20on%20the%20pain%20point%20of%20cognitive%20decline%2C%20which%20when%20not%20arrested%20early%20can%20quickly%20lead%20to%20dementia%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20like%20how%20natural%20ivory%20embodies%20resilience%2C%20durability%2C%20and%20timeless%20elegance%2C%20our%20startup%20empowers%20seniors%20to%20lead%20fulfilling%20lives%20in%20their%20later%20years.%20It%20also%20is%20a%20homage%20to%20Kerala%2C%20our%20home%20state%2C%20where%20majestic%20elephants%20are%20treasured%20as%20part%20of%20our%20rich%20heritage%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taking%20care%20of%20your%20parents'%20brain%20health%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345586%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9COur%20starting%20point%20was%20to%20build%20something%20that%20would%20help%20parents%20feel%20less%20isolated%20and%20lonely%20as%20they%20stayed%20away%20from%20their%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20scale%20of%20the%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20September%202023%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEstimates%20based%20on%20a%20recent%20multi-centric%20study%20reveal%20a%20dementia%20prevalence%20rate%20of%207.4%25%20among%20those%20aged%2060%20years%20and%20above%2C%20translating%20to%20nearly%209%20lakh%20Indians%20currently%20living%20with%20dementia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20an%20estimated%2088%20lakh%20in%202016%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337126%2Fmonitors-for-elderly-hemesh-chadalavada-invents-device-for-dementia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevalence%20of%20dementia%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20projected%20to%20increase%20to%201.7%20crore%20by%202036.%20The%20study%20titled%20%E2%80%98Prevalence%20of%20dementia%20in%20India%3A%20National%20and%20State%20estimates%20from%20a%20nationwide%20study%E2%80%99%20was%20published%20in%20July%20this%20year%20%5B2023%5D%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAlzheimer%E2%80%99s%20and%20Dementia%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20journal%20of%20the%20Alzheimer%E2%80%99s%20Association.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20experts%20at%20Ivory%2C%20%E2%80%9CLatest%20research%20estimates%20show%20that%20one%20person%20in%20India%20faces%20the%20risk%20of%20dementia%20every%2020%20seconds.%20Contributing%20factors%20such%20as%20loneliness%2C%20increased%20nuclear%20families%20and%20sedentary%20lifestyles%20have%20added%20to%20the%20problem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20their%20research%2C%20%E2%80%9CLatest%20reports%20show%20that%20cases%20have%20increased%20from%20an%20estimated%205.3%20million%20in%202020%20to%208.8%20million%20in%202023.%20Furthermore%2C%20adults%20aged%2050%20to%2070%2C%20even%20with%20mild%20cognitive%20impairment%2C%20face%20a%201%20in%203%20chance%20of%20progressing%20to%20dementia%20within%20five%20years%2C%20underscoring%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20heightened%20dialogue%20and%20action%20in%20neuro%20health.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20Issac%2C%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%20at%20Ivory%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHistorically%2C%20there%20has%20been%20insufficient%20attention%20and%20understanding%20of%20dementia%2C%20especially%20in%20India.%20The%20lack%20of%20symptom%20identification%20tools%20combined%20with%20scant%20access%20to%20high-quality%20neurological%20advice%20at%20the%20right%20time%20makes%20this%20a%20pressing%20problem%20for%20every%20Indian%20household%20with%20an%20ageing%20parent.%20Urban%20seniors%2C%20particularly%20those%20living%20alone%2C%20face%20challenges%20in%20monitoring%20their%20cognitive%20health%2C%20exacerbated%20by%20%5BCOVID-19%5D%20pandemic-induced%20isolation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%2C%20co-founder%20and%20chief%20product%20officer%2C%20Ivory%2C%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20Ivory%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20developing%20a%20pioneering%20platform%20dedicated%20to%20the%20cognitive%20wellness%20of%20seniors%20and%20cultivating%20healthy%20brain%20habits.%20We%20offer%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20interactive%20content%2C%20social%20games%2C%20neuroscience-backed%20assessments%2C%20and%20comprehensive%20wellness%20programmes%20aimed%20at%20enhancing%20cognitive%20well-being%20and%20mitigating%20the%20risk%20of%20brain-related%20ailments%20such%20as%20dementia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGetting%20to%20this%20point%2C%20however%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20easy.%20As%20Issac%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20first%20met%2C%20there%20were%20few%20ready%20reckoners%20and%20research%20available%20for%20companies%20who%20are%20building%20in%20age-tech%2C%20particularly%20in%20India%2C%20so%20it%20was%20not%20possible%20to%20take%20any%20existing%20learnings%20and%20apply%20them%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20seniors.%20That%20meant%20that%20we%20had%20to%20experiment%20with%20multiple%20product%20concepts%20parallelly%20before%20zeroing%20down%20on%20what%20would%20find%20mass%20pain-point%20resonance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntrepreneurship%20in%20the%20field%20of%20brain%20health%20is%20still%20at%20a%20nascent%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20built%20these%20learnings%2C%20we%20also%20realised%20that%20the%20VC%20ecosystem%20was%20still%20warming%20up%20to%20this%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20in%20the%20last%20six%20months%2C%20many%20funds%20have%20stepped%20forward%20to%20support%20AgeTech%20companies%2C%2018%20months%20ago%2C%20we%20had%20to%20build%20conviction%20about%20the%20opportunity%20of%20the%20AgeTech%20space%20in%20the%20venture%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20Ivory%20successfully%20raised%20%24500%2C000%20(Rs%204.13%20crore)%20in%20a%20funding%20round%20led%20by%20Capital%20A%2C%20an%20early-stage%20VC%20fund%2C%20in%20February%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20this%20fundraiser%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20bridge%20these%20gaps%20by%20offering%20a%20tech-driven%20platform%20that%20makes%20clinical%20tools%20and%20expertise%20for%20better%20brain%20health%20accessible%20to%20millions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Issac.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201741px)%20100vw%2C%201741px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FFact-Sheet-1711111397.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221741%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Navigating%20brain%20health%20in%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FFact-Sheet-1711111397.jpg%201741w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FFact-Sheet-1711111397-300x212.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FFact-Sheet-1711111397-500x353.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FFact-Sheet-1711111397-768x543.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FFact-Sheet-1711111397-1536x1085.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FFact-Sheet-1711111397-150x106.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345587%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221230%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIvory%20%E2%80%98Fact%20Sheet%E2%80%99%20on%20Dementia%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20seniors%20navigate%20brain%20health%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sumiti%20Saharan%2C%20a%20neuroscientist%20with%20over%2015%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20neurodegenerative%20disorders%20and%20dementia%20research%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%202050%2C%20one%20in%20five%20individuals%20will%20be%20elderly%20in%20India.%20The%20urgency%20for%20innovative%20solutions%20for%20dementia%20detection%20and%20management%20has%20become%20undeniable.%20Evidence-based%20solutions%20like%20Ivory%20offer%20a%20scalable%20and%20accessible%20mechanism%20for%20redefining%20the%20dementia%20care%20journey%20and%20empowering%20the%20elderly%20to%20live%20a%20healthy%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20does%20Ivory%20help%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341821%2Fsenior-citizen-couples-madhav-damle-matchmaking-agency-live-in-relationships-valentines-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esenior%20citizens%20%3C%2Fa%3Enavigate%20their%20brain%20health%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Rahul%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20concerned%20users%20and%20their%20families%20who%20want%20to%20understand%20if%20their%20memory%20lapses%20are%20stress%20related%20or%20something%20which%20warrants%20more%20attention%2C%20Ivory%20provides%20the%20equivalent%20of%20your%20annual%20health%20checkup%20for%20your%20brain.%20This%20checkup%20is%20done%20through%20cognitive%20assessments%20and%20neuro-psychological%20evaluations%2C%20which%20help%20you%20profile%20your%20brain%20health%20status%20and%20potential%20cognitive%20impairment%20or%20dementia%20risk.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTowards%20this%20end%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20partnered%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cognifit.com%2Fassessment-scientific-validation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECognifit%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20a%20scientifically%20validated%20and%20leading%20brain%20training%20and%20cognitive%20assessments%20company%20%E2%80%94%20to%20provide%20a%20starting%20point%20for%20tests.%20Their%20battery%20of%20tests%20have%20been%20developed%20with%20more%20than%2020%20years%20of%20inputs%20and%20research%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20Issac%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20cognitive%20test%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20many%20inputs%20which%20go%20into%20assessing%20someone%E2%80%99s%20cognitive%20decline%2C%20as%20every%20user%20is%20unique%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20cultural%20and%20sociological%20background.%20These%20assessments%20provide%20a%20cognitive%20report%20across%20various%20skills%2C%20and%20post%20that%2C%20more%20focussed%20assessments%20are%20carried%20out.%20Hence%2C%20every%20report%20that%20goes%20to%20the%20user%20is%20combined%20with%20a%20human%20interaction%20with%20a%20neuro%20counsellor%20to%20give%20a%20holistic%20risk%20assessment.%20Neuropsychologists%20then%20use%20these%20reports%20in%20consonance%20with%20their%20subjective%20examination%20of%20the%20patient%20to%20propose%20alternative%20lifestyle-based%20interventions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20neuropsychologist%20does%20employ%20a%20third-party%20assessment%20mechanism%20like%20a%20Mini-Mental%20State%20Examination%20(MMSE)%2C%20or%20a%20Montreal%20Cognitive%20Assessment%20(MoCA)%2C%20or%20an%20ICMR%20(Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research)-NCTB%20(Neuro%20Cognitive%20Tool%20Box)%2C%20or%20Addenbrooke%E2%80%99s%20Cognitive%20Examination%20(ACE)-III%20test.%20It%20is%20the%20combination%20of%20the%20test%20used%20along%20with%20a%20subjective%20interpretation%20and%20continuous%20tracking%20that%20makes%20for%20a%20more%20definitive%20assessment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20these%20cognitive%20and%20neuro-psychological%20assessments%2C%20counsellors%20hired%20by%20the%20startup%20suggest%20the%20next%20course%20of%20action%20which%20could%20include%20further%20clinical%20assessments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rahul%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20proactive%20users%2C%20who%20would%20just%20want%20to%20ensure%20they%20are%20keeping%20themselves%20mentally%20active%20and%20take%20a%20preventive%20approach%20towards%20brain%20health%2C%20we%20have%20our%20app%20which%20offers%20daily%20quizzes%2C%20brain%20games%2C%20and%20daily%20tips%20for%20an%20active%20lifestyle%20leading%20to%20reduced%20impairment%20risk.%20We%20have%20also%20developed%20a%20personalised%20brain%20workout%20daily%2C%20calibrated%20to%20improve%20the%20skills%20they%20lag%20in.%20The%20daily%20workout%20currently%20consists%20of%202%20games%20and%20a%20mini-assessment%20to%20measure%20progress.%20Going%20ahead%20we%20will%20be%20developing%20our%20proprietary%20workouts%20as%20we%20understand%20more%20about%20these%20users.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDepending%20on%20how%20the%20user%20performs%2C%20either%20the%20difficulty%20level%20or%20the%20games%20are%20then%20changed%20on%20an%20ongoing%20basis.%20The%20user%20will%20also%20get%20charts%20of%20progress%20that%20they%20can%20see%20across%20the%20skills%20he%20is