20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250621%2Fforest-fires-save-pradeep-mirase-ifs-similipal-malkangiri-environment-biodiversity-hero-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforest%20cover%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20state%20accounts%20for%2045%20percent%20compared%20to%20national%20forest%20cover%20of%20just%2021.67%20percent%20%E2%80%94%20this%20signifies%20the%20rich%20biological%20heritage%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20urgency%20to%20save%20one%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20carbon%20sinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20the%20need%20to%20preserve%20the%20rich%20flora%20and%20fauna%20of%20the%20state%2C%20in%202022%2C%20the%20Delhi-NCR-based%20NGO%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20(THF)%20began%20community-driven%20efforts%20to%20decrease%20forest%20fires%20in%20the%20state%20and%20promote%20environmental%20conservation%20and%20ecological%20balance.%20As%20part%20of%20this%20initiative%2C%20the%20foundation%20enlisted%20volunteer%20firefighters%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Pritam%20%E2%80%94%20to%20reduce%20forest%20fire%20occurrences.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1-1711021742.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Of%20the%20total%20forest%20cover%20of%20the%20state%2C%20more%20than%20one-third%20is%20prone%20to%20forest%20fires.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1-1711021742.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1-1711021742-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1-1711021742-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1-