20fire%20does%20not%20extend%20from%20one%20area%20to%20another.%20After%20making%20forest%20lines%2C%20we%20also%20throw%20sand%20to%20extinguish%20the%20fire.%20However%2C%20if%20the%20fire%20is%20on%20a%20large%20scale%2C%20we%20try%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20spreading%20further%20rather%20than%20extinguishing%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Following%20THF%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20many%20volunteers%20were%20provided%20comprehensive%20training%20to%20tackle%20forest%20fires.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345443%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFollowing%20THF%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20many%20volunteers%20were%20provided%20comprehensive%20training%20to%20tackle%20forest%20fires.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Pritam%2C%20THF%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20of%20preventing%20forest%20fire%20has%20seen%205%2C066%20young%20firefighters%20being%20trained%20in%201%2C000%20villages%20under%2010%20development%20blocks%20of%20Pauri%20Garhwal%2C%20Tehri%20Garhwal%2C%20Almora%2C%20and%20Bageshwar%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20T