o%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CCisco%E2%80%99s%20purpose%20is%20to%20%E2%80%98power%20an%20inclusive%20future%20for%20all%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20this%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20design%20of%20the%20initiatives%20we%20do.%20In%20our%20collaboration%20with%20Villgro%20on%20Tvaran%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20every%20startup%20gets%20to%20interact%20with%20subject%20matter%20experts%20from%20Cisco%20to%20build%20on%20their%20ideas%2C%20address%20roadblocks%2C%20and%20receive%20the%20needed%20mentorship%20and%20guidance%20to%20bring%20their%20vision%20to%20life.%20It%20also%20includes%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F308120%2Fstudent-maanya-singh-starts-incuba-naari-incubator-for-women-entrepreneurs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderstanding%20the%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20evolving%20technology%20landscape%20relevant%20to%20their%20sector.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20stories%20of%20the%20seven%20startups%20are%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20model%E2%80%99s%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbharatkrushiseva.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBharat%20Krushi%20Seva%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201014px)%20100vw%2C%201014px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBharat-Krushi-Seva_11zon-1710833201.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221014%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20at%20Bharat%20Krushi%20Seva%20has%20designed%20a%20mobile%20application%20that%20provides%20climate%20data%20to%20farmers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBharat-Krushi-Seva_11zon-1710833201.jpg%201014w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBharat-Krushi-Seva